Write a  program to find the reverse of the given without string using string library functions:

Input Format:

Input consist of 1 string.
Sample Input & Output:

hello

The reversed String is olleh

import java.util.Scanner;

public class Main
{
    public static void main(String[] args)
    {
        //creating an object for scanner class
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        
        //initializing the variables for user input
        String input = sc.nextLine();
        String [] result = input.split("");
        String ans = "";
        for (int i = input.length()-1 ; i >=0;i--){
            ans += result[i];
        }
        
        System.out.print("The reversed String is "+ans);
    }
}
